description: This top 10% Anurak purrs with a rating of 73, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 146, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, 3 for East, Box for South, and 1 for West. Anurak has the personality suit of hodler. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
